ZH: 我们常常去牧场上看牛。
EN: We often go to the ranch to see the cows.

ZH: 她在牧场上养了很多绵羊。
EN: She raised a lot of sheep on the ranch.

ZH: 这是一家非常大的牧场。
EN: This is a very big ranch.

ZH: 牧场主人给牛喂食。
EN: The ranch owner feeds the cows.

ZH: 在牧场上，我们可以呼吸到新鲜的空气。
EN: On the ranch, we can breathe fresh air.

ZH: 牧场上的牛都很健康。
EN: The cows on the ranch are all healthy.

ZH: 牧场主人为牲畜们打理了一个舒适的生活环境。
EN: The ranch owner created a comfortable living environment for the livestock.

ZH: 孩子们在牧场上体验到了农村的生活。
EN: The children experienced rural life on the ranch.

ZH: 牧场是一个放松心情的好地方。
EN: The ranch is a great place to relax.

ZH: 在这个牧场，他们养了很多的动物，包括马、牛和羊。
EN: They raise a lot of animals, including horses, cows, and sheep, on this ranch.

ZH: 牧场上有一个湖，供动物们喝水。
EN: There is a lake on the ranch for the animals to drink from.

ZH: 我们打算在牧场上举办一个野餐活动。
EN: We plan to have a picnic on the ranch.

ZH: 牧场是我最喜欢的地方之一。
EN: The ranch is one of my favorite places.

ZH: 他们在牧场上建了一个小屋，用来休息。
EN: They built a cabin on the ranch for resting.

ZH: 孩子们很喜欢去牧场玩耍。
EN: The children love to play on the ranch.

ZH: 这个牧场位于郊外，风景非常美丽。
EN: This ranch is located in the outskirts and has beautiful scenery.

ZH: 牧场主人每天都会照顾动物们的健康和生活。
EN: The ranch owner takes care of the animals' health and well-being every day.

ZH: 我们在牧场上看到了一只正在跑的小兔子。
EN: We saw a little rabbit running on the ranch.

ZH: 牧场上有很多野花，非常漂亮。
EN: There are many wildflowers on the ranch, very beautiful.

ZH: 牧场上的草地非常绿，非常适合动物们吃草。
EN: The grass on the ranch is very green and suitable for the animals to graze on.
